      <title>苹果的下一代超级智能手表将能够通过卫星发送短信</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apple-plans-apple-watch-ultra-3-next-year-with-satellite-texting-and-5g</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司计划在 2025 年为其智能手表引入卫星连接，并正在加紧开发血压功能，以吸引徒步旅行者和注重健康的消费者升级他们的设备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apple-plans-apple-watch-ultra-3-next-year-with-satellite-texting-and-5g</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激进分子威胁迫在眉睫，Tinder Parent Match 面临高标准转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/match-faces-high-bar-for-turnaround-as-activist-threat-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Match Group Inc. 将于周三举行首次投资者会议，投资者对此寄予厚望，活动人士和分析师正在等待该公司推出具体计划，以扭转其旗舰约会应用 Tinder 用户数量持续下滑的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/match-faces-high-bar-for-turnaround-as-activist-threat-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国网络安全公司受到美国制裁，员工遭指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-cybersecurity-firm-sanctioned-employee-charged-by-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对一家中国公司实施制裁，指控其为情报机构工作，并指控其一名员工入侵全球数千家企业的计算机系统，其中包括美国关键基础设施公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-cybersecurity-firm-sanctioned-employee-charged-by-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 建议微软购买比特币，但未能成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/microstrategy-s-mstr-saylor-pitch-for-microsoft-to-buy-bitcoin-falls-short</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使微策略公司 (MicroStrategy Inc.) 的迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 的个人呼吁也未能说服软件巨头微软公司跟随他的脚步投资比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/microstrategy-s-mstr-saylor-pitch-for-microsoft-to-buy-bitcoin-falls-short</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:29:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Alphabet 凭借 Willow 量子芯片取得突破，股价一路飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/alphabet-climbs-following-breakthrough-with-willow-quantum-chip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌母公司 Alphabet Inc. 周一宣布通过使用 Willow 量子芯片在量子计算方面取得重大进展，分析师对此表示赞赏，该公司股价随即创下 10 月份以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/alphabet-climbs-following-breakthrough-with-willow-quantum-chip</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:50:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光获 62 亿美元芯片订单，以刺激工厂扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/micron-gets-6-2-billion-chips-award-to-spur-plant-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府已达成最终协议，将从旨在促进美国半导体制造业发展的计划中向美光公司提供近 62 亿美元的补贴，使资金开始流向爱达荷州和纽约州的工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/micron-gets-6-2-billion-chips-award-to-spur-plant-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管增长乏力、面临关税风险，苹果股价仍大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apple-s-rally-is-unabated-by-sluggish-growth-and-tariff-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司是大型科技股中收入增长最慢的，而且在唐纳德·特朗普第二任期内面临关税相关风险。但这些因素均未拖累其股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apple-s-rally-is-unabated-by-sluggish-growth-and-tariff-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 11:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
